  <text>
    <body><div type="letter">
      <p>Dearest W--. All well here. H-- &amp; C-- go tomorrow. I am getting quite right again, &amp; this evening mean to begin a little Mathematics .-- Your Sisters have been most exceedingly affectionate &amp; kind.--</p>
      <p>The Avis Phoenix</p>
      <p>P.S. Charlotte also much better.</p>
    </div></body>
